<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-11-0043 </DOCNO><TEXT>A brief review is given of India's energy experience and its part in thedeveloping economy of India. Emphasis is paid to appropriate planningand the use, as far as possible, of locally available inputs. It is concludedthat for the development of the rural sector emphasis should be put onenergy plants which are low cost and appropriately sized for local needs.</TEXT></DOC>